snippet.title: Eloquent Countenance | RPG Maker Horror | No Commentary
snippet.description:
NOTE: I had to mute the audio from 53:40-57:38 due to copyright stuff. So it might sound odd. I apologize for the inconvenience. (Song was the one where they sing hallelujah.)

Game: Eloquent Countenance
Find the game here: https://racheldrawsthis.itch.io/eloquent-countenance
Original creator: racheldrawsthis
Release Date: 2022
Engine: RPG Maker MV
I do NOT own anything on this video, all credit to their respective creators.

If the creator wants me to take this down, please tell me.

...I had to try and upload this multiple times. I'm not going to try and write a description after that, my bad. I enjoyed the game and really liked the art. That's all I'll say. A nice and short enough RPG Maker Horror game for an evening.
